swapRateDimi(address).details: The swap rate offered the specified client, out of 10000. Standard Uniswapv2 behavior is "9970", i.e. a 0.3% fee is charged on swaps. "10000" is a fee-less swap (full value); "0" means no swap is possible (full value is confiscated). Numbers outside that range are invalid.
